data.description: Step into the epitome of modern comfort and timeless charm with this beautifully renovated all-brick ranch nestled on an expansive 3-acre lot in the heart of the south Fulton community. Boasting a full unfinished basement complete with a convenient chair lift, this home offers both versatility and convenience for all stages of life. The heart of the home resides in its bright and inviting kitchen, featuring sleek quartz countertops, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, including a gas range perfect for culinary enthusiasts. Adorned with elegant MOEN fixtures, the kitchen seamlessly flows into a spacious second living area, overlooking a stunning light-filled sunroom that beckons relaxing and enjoying the picturesque surroundings. Venture outdoors to discover your own private sanctuary within the fenced-in backyard, ideal for summer gatherings, gardening endeavors, or simply unwinding in tranquility. Meticulously cared for and cherished, this home radiates warmth and comfort, promising an exceptional living experience for homeowners and investors alike.  Don't miss this opportunity to make this meticulously crafted residence your own – a perfect blend of modern luxury and timeless appeal awaits within these walls.
